<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c5">ابن القاسم:</span> أنظر ج‍ ١ ص ٢٧<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c5">القاسم:</span> أنظر ج‍ ١ ص ٢٧١<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c5">القاضى:</span> أنظر ج‍ ٢ ص ٣٦١<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c5">ابن القاضى:</span> أنظر <span class="c2">«أبو العباس»</span> ج‍ ٤ ص ٣٦٧<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>